    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>
          Unplanned downtimes or quality issues cost millions. The Root Cause Agent ingests telemetry, MES data, and expert knowledge to identify the “why” behind deviations — and suggests corrective actions.
        </p>

        <h2>Process</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>Alert detected (e.g., defect spike in body shop).</li>
          <li>Root Cause Agent correlates signals with past incidents, supplier data, and machine logs.</li>
          <li>Probable causes ranked by likelihood.</li>
          <li>Proposed actions (maintenance, supplier notification, process tweak).</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>Key Benefits</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Reduces Mean Time to Resolution (MTTR).</li>
          <li>Preserves expert knowledge digitally.</li>
          <li>Scales across plants and suppliers.</li>
        </ul>
